WEBVTT

00:00:01.180 --> 00:00:03.016
I'm going.

00:00:04.184 --> 00:00:05.768
Hey, Ichigo!

00:00:06.144 --> 00:00:09.731
How do you intend
to get back there?

00:00:15.903 --> 00:00:17.405
Right on time!

00:00:17.989 --> 00:00:18.990
Let's go.

00:00:21.659 --> 00:00:23.911
Looking good there.

00:00:39.219 --> 00:00:41.889
You should be able to
do this now, Ichigo.

00:01:17.715 --> 00:01:18.759
You're the one.

00:01:40.364 --> 00:01:41.614
Nice.

00:01:42.698 --> 00:01:43.700
Come on up.

00:01:44.200 --> 00:01:47.037
I'll personally reforge it for you.

00:02:08.099 --> 00:02:12.854
<i>The blue skies above are hopelessly clear</i>

00:02:12.854 --> 00:02:18.026
<i>At my wit's end, I feel
a growing frustration</i>

00:02:18.443 --> 00:02:22.865
<i>As if to laugh at us hopeless cowards</i>

00:02:23.198 --> 00:02:26.617
<i>Countless eyes stare at us</i>

00:02:27.076 --> 00:02:32.957
<i>This soul of mine breaks again and again</i>

00:02:33.250 --> 00:02:36.169
<i>All I can do is hold it tight</i>

00:02:37.378 --> 00:02:42.425
<i>Until the day it turns to ash</i>

00:02:42.675 --> 00:02:45.304
<i>I've absorbed all of this sorrow</i>

00:02:45.429 --> 00:02:50.016
<i>It has shaped me, painted me</i>

00:02:50.141 --> 00:02:52.853
<i>But that's how we got here, right?</i>

00:02:52.978 --> 00:02:57.774
<i>One step at a time, just like breathing</i>

00:02:57.900 --> 00:03:00.318
<i>These countless scars on my palm</i>

00:03:00.443 --> 00:03:02.320
<i>That no longer fade</i>

00:03:02.445 --> 00:03:06.074
<i>Are my badge, my story</i>

00:03:06.366 --> 00:03:10.037
<i>I faced the fear and shred it to pieces</i>

00:03:10.162 --> 00:03:13.122
<i>And let it walk beside me once more</i>

00:03:13.122 --> 00:03:18.086
BLEACH: THOUSAND-YEAR BLOOD WAR

00:03:31.432 --> 00:03:33.266
SQUAD 10 BARRACKS -
TRAINING GROUNDS

00:03:33.268 --> 00:03:37.289
SQUAD 10 KENJUTSU INSTRUCTOR -
SHUTETSU NAGAKISO
You won't be able to cut down
the Quincies with those swings!

00:03:37.313 --> 00:03:38.314
- Yes, sir!
- Yes, sir!

00:03:43.319 --> 00:03:44.612
Captain Hitsugaya!

00:03:46.156 --> 00:03:47.366
What brings you here?

00:03:48.532 --> 00:03:50.284
I'd like for you to train me.

00:03:50.451 --> 00:03:51.245
What?

00:03:51.246 --> 00:03:53.288
My Bankai was stolen.

00:03:54.038 --> 00:03:56.207
If I'm to fight
using only Zanjutsu,

00:03:56.500 --> 00:03:58.180
then I must retrain myself
from the basics.

00:04:01.379 --> 00:04:05.550
<i>After the battle against Aizen,
I thoroughly refined my Bankai...</i>

00:04:06.259 --> 00:04:08.595
<i>until it could be called
a true Bankai.</i>

00:04:09.887 --> 00:04:12.432
<i>However, my Bankai was stolen...</i>

00:04:13.307 --> 00:04:14.892
<i>I must let go of what's been lost.</i>

00:04:15.310 --> 00:04:17.812
<i>There's no time to be dreaming
of getting it back.</i>

00:04:18.689 --> 00:04:21.024
<i>Right now, I need to look ahead.</i>

00:04:22.401 --> 00:04:25.110
RUKON DISTRICT - OUTSKIRTS

00:04:25.112 --> 00:04:26.271
Why have you brought me here?

00:04:27.363 --> 00:04:30.199
Shuhei,
I want you to master Bankai.

00:04:30.574 --> 00:04:31.576
What?

00:04:32.160 --> 00:04:34.704
My Bankai wasn't stolen this time,

00:04:35.247 --> 00:04:37.307
but there's no guarantee
it won't happen the next time.

00:04:37.331 --> 00:04:39.625
The more Soul Reapers
who can do Bankai, the better.

00:04:42.504 --> 00:04:44.130
Hollowfy, Mashiro!

00:04:44.338 --> 00:04:46.298
SQUAD 9 LIEUTENANT -
MASHIRO KUNA
Okay!

00:04:46.300 --> 00:04:48.759
SQUAD 9 LIEUTENANT -
MASHIRO KUNA
Transform!

00:04:48.884 --> 00:04:50.262
W-Wait, Kuna!

00:04:50.595 --> 00:04:51.637
You better watch out.

00:04:52.180 --> 00:04:54.098
Mashiro is strong
when she's Hollowfied.

00:04:54.598 --> 00:04:58.435
I think mastering your Bankai
is the only way you won't die.

00:04:58.437 --> 00:05:00.937
Captain Muguruma,
you can't expect me to just...

00:05:00.939 --> 00:05:02.024
Hi-yah!

00:05:06.235 --> 00:05:07.237
You idiot.

00:05:07.446 --> 00:05:08.904
I told you to watch out.

00:05:09.322 --> 00:05:10.615
That's right!

00:05:10.824 --> 00:05:14.870
A lieutenant shouldn't disobey
a <i>super</i> lieutenant!

00:05:15.370 --> 00:05:18.247
I hope you're not thinking
she won't kill you for real.

00:05:18.874 --> 00:05:21.084
I'm not soft like Tosen was.

00:05:24.254 --> 00:05:27.298
Hold on, Captain Muguruma...

00:05:28.216 --> 00:05:31.552
I've always looked up to
and respected you.

00:05:32.762 --> 00:05:33.764
But still...

00:05:35.057 --> 00:05:39.394
you have no right
to bad-mouth Captain Tosen!

00:05:42.064 --> 00:05:44.982
DEPARTMENT OF
RESEARCH & DEVELOPMENT

00:05:44.983 --> 00:05:48.944
DEPARTMENT OF R&D -
CONTROL ROOM Hey.

00:05:49.237 --> 00:05:50.197
Mr. Akon!

00:05:50.197 --> 00:05:52.197
Is it okay for you
to walk around already?!

00:05:52.199 --> 00:05:54.951
Of course not.
It still hurts.

00:05:55.285 --> 00:05:58.454
But I'm not the type to be
lying around in bed all day.

00:05:59.622 --> 00:06:00.622
Where's the Captain?

00:06:00.624 --> 00:06:01.708
About that...

00:06:02.041 --> 00:06:05.086
He's been cooped up
in his office with the Lieutenant

00:06:05.086 --> 00:06:07.338
ever since the Quincy attack.

00:06:07.672 --> 00:06:09.757
He hasn't come out since then?

00:06:10.091 --> 00:06:11.093
That's right.

00:06:23.271 --> 00:06:24.271
Is something wrong?

00:06:24.523 --> 00:06:27.149
The Captain has been cooped up
for more than 24 hours,

00:06:27.149 --> 00:06:28.901
yet the Surveillance Bugs
remain inactive.

00:06:29.444 --> 00:06:31.696
- That's never happened before.
- What?

00:06:32.029 --> 00:06:34.658
Either a crisis has occurred
within the Captain's office

00:06:35.033 --> 00:06:38.119
or he's conducting experiments that
he doesn't want anyone to see

00:06:38.120 --> 00:06:39.829
through the Surveillance Bugs.

00:06:40.454 --> 00:06:42.331
At any rate,
I'm going to take a look.

00:06:44.375 --> 00:06:46.086
Mr. Akon, what is that...?

00:06:46.377 --> 00:06:49.004
It's a camera I planted
in the Captain's office.

00:06:49.004 --> 00:06:50.548
- But that's—!
- Not now.

00:06:51.091 --> 00:06:52.091
I'm getting a visual!

00:06:52.216 --> 00:06:53.968
<i>It will use its existing tissue
as a host</i>

00:06:53.968 --> 00:06:55.552
<i>to give birth
to a new Ashisogijizo...</i>

00:06:55.553 --> 00:06:57.180
What the hell is that...?!

00:06:58.139 --> 00:07:01.225
What the hell is
the Captain creating?!

00:07:03.437 --> 00:07:06.439
"OMAEDA" Big Brother!

00:07:07.314 --> 00:07:10.317
Where are you, Big Brother?!

00:07:11.903 --> 00:07:12.903
Big Brother!

00:07:14.363 --> 00:07:17.658
Big Brother!
Please play ball with me!

00:07:17.658 --> 00:07:19.326
No!

00:07:23.038 --> 00:07:26.166
Wait!
Don't cry, Mareyo!

00:07:26.168 --> 00:07:29.463
I... umm...

00:07:31.548 --> 00:07:33.216
Want to play <i>kemari</i>?

00:07:33.966 --> 00:07:34.968
Yes!

00:07:35.634 --> 00:07:37.178
Here goes!

00:07:37.387 --> 00:07:40.973
Wow!
That's amazing, Big Brother!

00:07:41.348 --> 00:07:43.641
- I guess the Captain
- Look at it go!

00:07:43.642 --> 00:07:46.646
Decided not to take me with her...

00:07:55.654 --> 00:07:57.240
Who's there?

00:07:58.408 --> 00:08:01.911
It's been a long time, Great Elder.

00:08:04.122 --> 00:08:05.706
Sajin, huh?

00:08:05.915 --> 00:08:09.418
You've got some nerve
coming back here.

00:08:10.086 --> 00:08:12.297
What do you want, Sajin?

00:08:13.798 --> 00:08:18.470
Great Elder, I have come to learn
our clan's secret technique.

00:08:25.309 --> 00:08:27.269
Don't be ridiculous.

00:08:28.230 --> 00:08:31.105
You shamelessly donned
a hat and armor

00:08:31.106 --> 00:08:33.359
and pretended to be human

00:08:33.360 --> 00:08:37.905
because you were embarrassed
by our clan's appearance.

00:08:38.240 --> 00:08:41.326
How dare you make demands of me.

00:08:41.618 --> 00:08:42.619
Please take a look.

00:08:43.035 --> 00:08:44.913
I no longer wear a hat...

00:08:45.663 --> 00:08:48.707
The world has changed
in the past few decades.

00:08:49.375 --> 00:08:53.169
I sense that the world
has reached a point

00:08:53.171 --> 00:08:56.048
where our clan
can live out in the open.

00:08:56.924 --> 00:08:59.969
And that very world
is currently under threat!

00:08:59.970 --> 00:09:01.971
Shut your mouth!

00:09:03.181 --> 00:09:05.640
You have it all wrong.

00:09:05.642 --> 00:09:08.061
The world will never perish.

00:09:08.227 --> 00:09:12.606
Only the bearer of it will change.

00:09:13.399 --> 00:09:15.275
Our clan won't change.

00:09:15.277 --> 00:09:17.152
Regardless of whoever
claims the world,

00:09:17.153 --> 00:09:20.029
we will continue
to live in the shadows.

00:09:20.030 --> 00:09:22.450
I'm telling you we can change that!

00:09:23.243 --> 00:09:25.120
We <i>must</i> change it

00:09:25.412 --> 00:09:27.451
for the sake of our children,
and our grandchildren.

00:09:27.496 --> 00:09:29.291
It won't change.

00:09:29.707 --> 00:09:31.625
Nor is there a need to.

00:09:32.501 --> 00:09:37.716
Whoever the world belongs to,
it's none of our concern.

00:09:37.881 --> 00:09:39.049
Great Elder!

00:09:42.303 --> 00:09:44.471
Don't you understand, Sajin?

00:09:45.056 --> 00:09:50.311
I'm telling you not to disrupt
the peace we have.

00:09:50.312 --> 00:09:53.273
If you cannot do that...

00:09:53.815 --> 00:09:57.067
I shall crush you.

00:09:58.403 --> 00:10:00.113
Bring it on!

00:10:13.543 --> 00:10:14.751
This is why Hoohden
was built on a cliff!

00:10:14.753 --> 00:10:17.629
HOOHDEN - FORGE
This is why Hoohden
was built on a cliff!

00:10:17.630 --> 00:10:21.301
A Bankai cannot be reforged
without all these waters.

00:10:22.719 --> 00:10:25.263
Now brace yourself, Ichigo.

00:10:25.846 --> 00:10:30.434
This is where you
and your Zanpakuto, Zangetsu...

00:10:32.269 --> 00:10:34.022
must say goodbye!

00:10:51.456 --> 00:10:56.335
Come on, everybody!
Let's begin!

00:10:56.336 --> 00:11:00.923
Welcome to my show!

00:11:01.216 --> 00:11:02.424
- Yessir!
- Yessir...

00:11:06.804 --> 00:11:09.349
The Nimaiya Bodyguards are here!

00:11:12.851 --> 00:11:15.230
Why are you just
standing there staring?

00:11:15.522 --> 00:11:18.732
When I said "everybody,"
that includes you too...

00:11:19.192 --> 00:11:20.192
Asauchi.

00:11:28.909 --> 00:11:30.787
What is going on...?!

00:11:31.370 --> 00:11:33.331
Let's party time!

00:11:43.216 --> 00:11:44.551
Ready!

00:11:45.176 --> 00:11:47.345
NIMAIYA BODYGUARD -
NONOMI NOMINO

00:11:47.886 --> 00:11:48.888
All right!

00:11:56.019 --> 00:11:58.105
NIMAIYA BODYGUARD -
MERA HIUCHIGASHIMA

00:11:59.816 --> 00:12:00.984
I hate this.

00:12:01.234 --> 00:12:02.652
It's such a hassle...

00:12:03.235 --> 00:12:06.447
I can't believe I'm being dragged
into this mess again...

00:12:06.740 --> 00:12:08.700
NIMAIYA BODYGUARD -
TOKIE TONOKAWA

00:12:09.158 --> 00:12:10.743
What a horrible life...

00:12:10.744 --> 00:12:12.535
Stop complaining, Ms. Tokie!

00:12:12.537 --> 00:12:14.998
This is our job, remember?

00:12:15.123 --> 00:12:16.124
Here goes!

00:12:17.125 --> 00:12:18.668
There!

00:12:20.169 --> 00:12:21.296
Got you!

00:12:22.129 --> 00:12:24.048
NIMAIYA BODYGUARD -
HASUKA HASHIHARA

00:12:34.100 --> 00:12:36.351
NIMAIYA BODYGUARD -
TSUMIKO TSUCHIMIYA

00:12:40.565 --> 00:12:41.566
Now then...

00:12:42.649 --> 00:12:44.443
Let's get started.

00:12:53.620 --> 00:12:56.121
What are you thinking
as you see this, Go-Ichi?

00:12:57.749 --> 00:13:00.375
Well, it's much brighter now,

00:13:00.876 --> 00:13:03.504
so maybe you should have
left your sunglasses on...

00:13:03.797 --> 00:13:05.673
You fool!

00:13:06.633 --> 00:13:08.467
If I kept my sunglasses on...

00:13:08.842 --> 00:13:11.888
I wouldn't be able to see
the color of the flames!

00:13:13.764 --> 00:13:15.850
Have you figured it out, Go-Ichi?

00:13:18.769 --> 00:13:21.562
The reason why
this Asauchi turned white

00:13:21.563 --> 00:13:23.566
the moment it touched you...

00:13:24.859 --> 00:13:25.860
No...

00:13:26.193 --> 00:13:27.986
I bet this is what
crossed your mind...

00:13:29.197 --> 00:13:31.490
"It reminds me of
the Hollow within me."

00:13:35.202 --> 00:13:38.413
That's right.
This guy <i>is</i> the Hollow within you.

00:13:39.123 --> 00:13:44.546
That Asauchi became the catalyst
to draw this Zanpakuto out.

00:13:46.880 --> 00:13:52.095
I'm saying that this Hollow
is your Zanpakuto, Go-Ichi!

00:13:55.682 --> 00:13:59.476
Aizen created the Hollow
known as "White"

00:13:59.852 --> 00:14:03.105
by layering countless
Soul Reaper souls.

00:14:03.398 --> 00:14:08.027
Oddly enough, that is the same
method I use to create my Asauchi.

00:14:08.403 --> 00:14:11.028
That Hollow entered your body

00:14:11.029 --> 00:14:15.118
and melded with
your natural Soul Reaper powers...

00:14:15.826 --> 00:14:18.203
becoming your Zanpakuto.

00:14:19.330 --> 00:14:20.373
Hold on a second...

00:14:20.706 --> 00:14:22.667
are you saying that
Old Man Zangetsu is...

00:14:23.167 --> 00:14:24.168
I told you, didn't I?

00:14:25.836 --> 00:14:28.798
That you will be saying goodbye
to "Zangetsu."

00:14:29.631 --> 00:14:32.259
Yes, you already know...

00:14:34.386 --> 00:14:37.514
about the man
who has been pretending to be

00:14:37.514 --> 00:14:40.768
your Zanpakuto within your soul!

00:14:50.736 --> 00:14:53.072
Old Man... Zangetsu...

00:14:54.573 --> 00:14:58.201
Go-Ichi, you know that man.

00:14:58.494 --> 00:14:59.495
Of course, I do...

00:15:00.245 --> 00:15:02.749
- He's Zangetsu—
- No, look closer.

00:15:03.875 --> 00:15:10.255
You've seen that man up close
with your own eyes quite recently...

00:15:10.505 --> 00:15:13.301
as the enemy who destroyed
the Soul Society!

00:15:15.219 --> 00:15:17.346
That man is <i>not</i>
your Soul Reaper powers.

00:15:17.804 --> 00:15:22.851
He is your <i>Quincy</i> powers
taking the form of...

00:15:23.269 --> 00:15:26.397
Yhwach from a thousand years ago!

00:15:31.152 --> 00:15:33.779
<i>I've been trying
not to think about it...</i>

00:15:35.697 --> 00:15:36.698
<i>That day,</i>

00:15:37.658 --> 00:15:39.701
<i>when I first confronted him...</i>

00:15:41.537 --> 00:15:44.081
<i>I felt as if I was drawn there.</i>

00:15:45.582 --> 00:15:49.711
<i>I had been trying
not to ask myself why.</i>

00:15:51.004 --> 00:15:53.881
<i>About why I was able to
go straight to him</i>

00:15:53.883 --> 00:15:55.342
<i>without knowing anything...</i>

00:15:56.134 --> 00:15:59.138
<i>Or why I thought he was
the most important enemy...</i>

00:16:02.140 --> 00:16:03.142
<i>And finally...</i>

00:16:04.519 --> 00:16:06.562
<i>why the first time I saw him...</i>

00:16:08.105 --> 00:16:10.607
<i>he reminded me of someone I know.</i>

00:16:22.787 --> 00:16:23.870
Zangetsu!

00:16:32.337 --> 00:16:35.091
What is going on, Zangetsu?

00:16:36.259 --> 00:16:38.052
It's just as you heard.

00:16:38.302 --> 00:16:39.846
And...

00:16:41.139 --> 00:16:42.597
I am not Zangetsu.

00:16:56.738 --> 00:16:59.323
Then you really are... Yhwach?

00:17:00.365 --> 00:17:01.826
Are you really...

00:17:02.451 --> 00:17:03.911
not Zangetsu?

00:17:04.327 --> 00:17:08.790
I am the source of the Quincy power
within you.

00:17:09.166 --> 00:17:13.045
I am Yhwach, yet I am not.

00:17:13.046 --> 00:17:14.337
I don't get it!

00:17:15.088 --> 00:17:16.798
Are you my enemy
or are you my ally?!

00:17:17.215 --> 00:17:19.676
Was everything
you said to me a lie?!

00:17:20.303 --> 00:17:21.554
Answer me!

00:17:25.182 --> 00:17:28.185
I'm not an enemy or an ally.

00:17:29.144 --> 00:17:31.939
But there were no lies
in my words to you.

00:17:32.647 --> 00:17:35.108
Except for the name I told you.

00:17:36.903 --> 00:17:40.073
Ichigo, I know you've seen it.

00:17:41.156 --> 00:17:45.076
Whenever I taught you
how to use your Zanpakuto,

00:17:45.077 --> 00:17:48.205
I always had help from the Hollow...

00:17:49.123 --> 00:17:53.336
Whenever you couldn't handle
your Zanpakuto's power...

00:17:53.795 --> 00:17:57.298
When you were truly in danger
of losing your life...

00:17:58.257 --> 00:18:00.884
The one that saved your life...

00:18:01.219 --> 00:18:02.470
was not me,

00:18:03.096 --> 00:18:05.138
but the Hollow.

00:18:06.432 --> 00:18:09.810
I didn't want you to become
a Soul Reaper.

00:18:10.269 --> 00:18:13.188
That is why I suppressed
your true power,

00:18:13.189 --> 00:18:15.147
which had not fully matured...

00:18:15.148 --> 00:18:19.028
and became the center
of your power.

00:18:19.487 --> 00:18:21.279
- Why?
- "Why"?

00:18:21.864 --> 00:18:26.076
I wished to keep you
far from danger, and from conflict.

00:18:26.576 --> 00:18:28.203
What is there to question?

00:18:29.163 --> 00:18:31.039
If you became a Soul Reaper,

00:18:31.414 --> 00:18:34.042
you would be dragged into battle
whether you wanted to or not.

00:18:34.626 --> 00:18:36.336
You would get hurt...

00:18:37.003 --> 00:18:38.548
You would suffer...

00:18:39.339 --> 00:18:43.176
And eventually,
I would have to kill you...

00:18:43.469 --> 00:18:46.221
with my own hands.

00:18:57.482 --> 00:19:00.153
I couldn't let you become
a Soul Reaper.

00:19:00.694 --> 00:19:03.530
If you did,
I would have to kill you.

00:19:04.406 --> 00:19:06.200
That's what I thought...

00:19:07.117 --> 00:19:11.122
However, you chose the path
of a Soul Reaper.

00:19:12.205 --> 00:19:15.040
You were given an opportunity
and honed your strength...

00:19:15.041 --> 00:19:16.960
You suffered and got hurt,

00:19:16.961 --> 00:19:20.088
yet still continued to travel down
that path of your own free will.

00:19:21.339 --> 00:19:27.430
As I watched you, I could almost
hear my heart wavering.

00:19:29.848 --> 00:19:32.683
Eventually, rather than try to
keep you away

00:19:32.684 --> 00:19:34.186
from the Soul Reapers,

00:19:34.436 --> 00:19:38.356
my heart leaned towards
supporting your decision.

00:19:39.901 --> 00:19:43.403
And now, I stand here...

00:19:47.032 --> 00:19:50.994
feeling the joy of stepping away
from you...

00:19:52.163 --> 00:19:55.249
Ichigo... you've become strong.

00:19:56.000 --> 00:20:01.213
I've been able to see your growth
right by your side.

00:20:02.964 --> 00:20:06.176
Nothing could make me happier.

00:20:09.430 --> 00:20:11.056
I am satisfied.

00:20:11.057 --> 00:20:13.726
W-Wait, Zangetsu!

00:20:14.434 --> 00:20:15.603
I still—!

00:20:29.741 --> 00:20:30.742
Ichigo...

00:20:31.326 --> 00:20:36.038
What you've been using is merely
a fragment of your power

00:20:36.039 --> 00:20:38.875
that I couldn't suppress.

00:20:40.169 --> 00:20:44.673
You can now fight
with your own power.

00:20:46.424 --> 00:20:47.593
Take it.

00:20:48.009 --> 00:20:51.263
That is your true Zanpakuto...

00:20:52.597 --> 00:20:54.057
<i>That</i> is Zangetsu.

00:20:59.105 --> 00:21:01.691
<i>You're right.
There were no lies...</i>

00:21:03.025 --> 00:21:04.359
<i>Not in his words...</i>

00:21:05.111 --> 00:21:06.237
<i>Or in your words...</i>

00:21:07.821 --> 00:21:11.241
<i>You used a Quincy's shadow
to help me.</i>

00:21:12.159 --> 00:21:16.038
<i>You used a Quincy's blood
to stop mine.</i>

00:21:17.038 --> 00:21:19.833
<i>And you lent me
the power of a Quincy</i>

00:21:19.834 --> 00:21:22.086
<i>to help me win when I was weak.</i>

00:21:24.547 --> 00:21:25.548
<i>Zangetsu...</i>

00:21:26.632 --> 00:21:29.050
<i>I don't care who you are.</i>

00:21:30.260 --> 00:21:32.137
<i>You might try to deny it, but...</i>

00:21:33.138 --> 00:21:34.140
<i>You...</i>

00:21:34.765 --> 00:21:35.766
<i>and him...</i>

00:21:36.308 --> 00:21:38.435
<i>are both Zangetsu to me.</i>

00:21:39.478 --> 00:21:42.147
<i>Let's just agree to that, okay?</i>

00:21:43.231 --> 00:21:44.232
<i>Zangetsu...</i>

00:21:56.453 --> 00:21:58.872
What are you doing?!
Your hands will...

00:21:58.873 --> 00:22:00.165
It's all good.

00:22:01.083 --> 00:22:02.500
Right, Go-Ichi?

00:22:03.169 --> 00:22:04.670
I was just thinking the same thing.

00:22:05.253 --> 00:22:11.218
That it would be complete
once you poured your soul into it.

00:22:11.844 --> 00:22:14.888
Now pull it out, Go-Ichi!

00:22:16.390 --> 00:22:19.477
That's your Zanpakuto!

00:22:30.320 --> 00:22:32.781
- The sea...
- It evaporated!

00:22:33.281 --> 00:22:34.741
Well, Go-Ichi?

00:22:35.742 --> 00:22:37.702
Think you can get along?

00:22:39.997 --> 00:22:42.833
With those Zangetsu...

00:22:44.210 --> 00:22:46.586
<i>Two</i>...Zanpakuto?!

00:22:46.586 --> 00:22:48.047
Amazing!

00:22:48.255 --> 00:22:51.133
Yup.
They were both real.

00:22:54.095 --> 00:22:55.136
<i>Zangetsu...</i>

00:22:56.638 --> 00:22:59.599
<i>I won't ask you to lend me
your strength anymore.</i>

00:23:02.060 --> 00:23:04.063
<i>I won't tell you
to stay out of my way, either.</i>

00:23:06.190 --> 00:23:09.484
<i>And I won't ask you guys
to fight alongside me.</i>

00:23:13.739 --> 00:23:16.659
<i>I'll fight on my own.</i>

00:23:22.664 --> 00:23:24.500
<i>Thank you, Zangetsu.</i>

00:23:27.127 --> 00:23:28.128
<i>You are...</i>

00:23:28.753 --> 00:23:29.755
<i>me.</i>

00:23:37.555 --> 00:23:40.348
You've returned, Haschwalth.

00:23:41.142 --> 00:23:42.143
And the subject?

00:23:43.853 --> 00:23:44.854
Right here.

00:23:54.238 --> 00:23:55.405
Welcome...

00:23:56.281 --> 00:23:57.700
Uryu Ishida.

00:24:01.036 --> 00:24:03.788
Now, let us fight together...

00:24:05.332 --> 00:24:07.292
my son.

